OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer and Donald Trump had
OL,7,Fa "constructive" phone call on Sunday
OL,8,Fevening, where they agreed that the
OL,9,Freopening of the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,10,F"essential" - as the US president's 48-
OL,11,Fhour deadline to Iran looms.
OL,13,FTrump issued Iran the deadline to
OL,14,Ffully open the critical shipping route
OL,15,F- which around one fifth of the
OL,16,Fworld's oil passes through - on
OL,17,FSaturday, and threatened to
OL,18,F"obliterate" the country's power
OL,19,Fplants if it does not comply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FIn response, the speaker of Iran's
OL,7,Fparliament warned that the regime
OL,8,Fwould target and destroy critical
OL,9,Finfrastructure, energy infrastructure,
OL,10,Fand oil facilities throughout the
OL,11,Fregion in an "irreversible manner",
OL,12,Fwith Iranian media later publishing a
OL,13,Flist of such sites.
OL,15,FThe threat by Tehran puts at risk both
OL,16,Felectrical supplies and water in
OL,17,Fregion, as desert nations have their
OL,18,Fpower stations next to desalination
OL,19,Fplants crucial for supplying drinking
OL,20,Fwater.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FStarmer and Trump spoke for 20 minutes
OL,7,Fand agreed that reopening the Strait
OL,8,Fis essential to "ensure stability in
OL,9,Fthe global energy market", a Downing
OL,10,FStreet spokesperson said.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
