OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FTrump's self-declared deadline expires
OL,7,Fat 11.44pm (UK time) on Monday,
OL,8,Ffurther raising the stakes of the
OL,9,Fongoing conflict, which has disrupted
OL,10,Fglobal energy supplies, and sent oil
OL,11,Fprices soaring over $113 a barrel on
OL,12,FMonday morning.
OL,14,FThe death toll from the war has risen
OL,15,Fto more than 1,500 people in Iran,
OL,16,Fmore than 1,000 people in Lebanon, 15
OL,17,Fin Israel and 13 US military members,
OL,18,Fas well as a number of civilians on
OL,19,Fland and sea in the Gulf region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FIsrael began began what it called "a
OL,7,Fwide-scale wave of strikes targeting
OL,8,FIranian terror regime infrastructure"
OL,9,Fearly on Monday.
OL,11,FStarmer and Trump speak hours after
OL,12,Fpresident mocks PM
OL,14,FTrump and Starmer had a "constructive"
OL,15,Fconversation Sunday and agreed to
OL,16,Fspeak again, a Downing Street
OL,17,Fspokesperson said.
OL,26,@pD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
