PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"They agreed that reopening the Strait
OL,7,Fof Hormuz was essential to ensure
OL,8,Fstability in the global energy
OL,9,Fmarket," they said.
OL,11,FThe phone call took place hours after
OL,12,Fthe president reshared a sketch from
OL,13,Fthe new British version of comedy show
OL,14,FSaturday Night Live, which saw a
OL,15,Ffrightened Starmer asking Deputy PM
OL,16,FDavid Lammy for advice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"What if Donald shouts at me? What do
OL,7,FI say Lammy?" the actor playing
OL,8,FStarmer says in the clip, before
OL,9,Fadding: "Oh crumbs, I just hate
OL,10,Fconflict."
OL,12,FTrump issued Iran the 48-hour deadline
OL,13,Fon Saturday evening, declaring that
OL,14,Fthe US would "obliterate" their power
OL,15,Fplants if it did not comply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
