PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"If Iran doesn't FULLY OPEN, WITHOUT
OL,7,FTHREAT, the Strait of Hormuz, within
OL,8,F48 HOURS from this exact point in
OL,9,Ftime, the United States of America
OL,10,Fwill hit and obliterate their various
OL,11,FPOWER PLANTS, STARTING WITH THE
OL,12,FBIGGEST ONE FIRST!" Trump posted on
OL,13,FTruth Social.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
