PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FTrump also said on Sunday the US was
OL,7,Fgetting "very close" to meeting its
OL,8,Fobjectives in the war, such as
OL,9,Fdestroying the regime's missile
OL,10,Fcapacity, eliminating their navy and
OL,11,Fair force, and ending nuclear
OL,12,Fcapabilities, adding that the Strait
OL,13,Fof Hormuz would need to be "guarded"
OL,14,Fonce the conflict ended.
OL,16,F"The Hormuz Strait will have to be
OL,17,Fguarded and policed, as necessary, by
OL,18,Fother Nations who use it ` The United
OL,19,FStates does not!" Trump wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"If asked, we will help these
OL,7,FCountries in their Hormuz efforts, but
OL,8,Fit shouldn't be necessary once Iran's
OL,9,Fthreat is eradicated. Importantly, it
OL,10,Fwill be an easy Military Operation for
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FIran threatens to hit power plants in
OL,14,Fretaliation
OL,16,FIranian media published a list of
OL,17,Fpower plants in Gulf Arab states after
OL,18,Fthe regime warned it would strike such
OL,19,Ffacilities if Trump follows through on
OL,20,Fhis threat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
