CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FThe list, including the United Arab
OL,7,FEmirates' nuclear power plant, was
OL,8,Fpublished by Fars News Agency, which
OL,9,Fhas close ties to the Islamic
OL,10,FRevolutionary Guard Corps (IRGC), and
OL,11,FIran's judiciary news agency Mizan.
OL,13,FThe UAE's Barakah nuclear power plant
OL,14,Fhas four reactors out in the western
OL,15,Fdeserts of the country near its border
OL,16,Fwith Saudi Arabia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
