PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FThe IRGC said on Monday Iran would
OL,7,Frespond by hitting power plants in all
OL,8,Fareas that supply electricity to
OL,9,FAmerican bases, "as well as the
OL,10,Feconomic, industrial and energy
OL,11,Finfrastructures in which Americans
OL,12,Fhave shares."
OL,14,F"Do not doubt that we will do this,"
OL,15,Fit said in a statement read on Iranian
OL,16,Fstate television.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FThe IRGC has also threated to close
OL,7,Fthe Strait of Hormuz entirely. At
OL,8,Fpresent, transits are down by 94.2%
OL,9,Fsince the war began on February 28,
OL,10,Fdata from Maritime AI company Windward
OL,11,Fshows.
OL,13,F"We did not start this war and will
OL,14,Fnot initiate it now, but if the enemy
OL,15,Fharms our power plants, we will do
OL,16,Fwhatever is necessary to defend our
OL,17,Fcountry and national interests,"
OL,18,FIranian Armed Forces spokesman
OL,19,FLieutenant Colonel Ebrahim Zolfaqari
OL,20,Fsaid on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"The uninterrupted process of
OL,7,Fdestroying the mentioned targets will
OL,8,Fbegin, and nothing will stop the
OL,9,Fcontinuation of our operations against
OL,10,FUS and allied energy, oil, and
OL,11,Findustrial infrastructure in the
OL,12,Fregion."
OL,14,FMultiple countries targeted by strikes
OL,15,Fovernight
OL,17,FAirstrikes were reported in Lebanon
OL,18,FSunday night into Monday morning,
OL,19,FLebanon's state news agency said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
