PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FThe Israel Defense Forces said it had
OL,7,Fbegun "a wide-scale wave of strikes
OL,8,Ftargeting Iranian terror regime
OL,9,Finfrastructure" in Tehran during the
OL,10,Fearly hours of Monday morning.
OL,12,FAn Indian national in the UAE was hurt
OL,13,Fby falling shrapnel on Monday after a
OL,14,Fballistic missile over an air base in
OL,15,FAbu Dhabi was intercepted, its
OL,16,Fauthorities said.
OL,18,FSaudi Arabia's Defence Ministry also
OL,19,Fsaid it had intercepted a missile
OL,20,Ftargeting its capital Riyadh, while
OL,21,Fanother struck an "uninhabited area".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FBoth Bahrain and Kuwait sounded
OL,7,Fmissile alerts early Monday over
OL,8,Fincoming Iranian fire.
OL,10,FMillions displayed as impact felt
OL,11,Facross Asia and Africa
OL,13,FA senior United Nations official has
OL,14,Fsaid the war has a "far reaching"
OL,15,Fimpact on millions of people,
OL,16,Fparticularly in developing countries
OL,17,Fin Asia and Africa.
OL,26,@vD@TOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30617
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,F"Our world is the most violent it has
OL,7,Fbeen since the Second World War,"
OL,8,FJorge Moreira da Silva, executive
OL,9,Fdirector of the UN Office for Project
OL,10,FServices, said.
OL,12,FThe war has displaced 3.2 million
OL,13,Fpeople in Iran and 1 million in
OL,14,FLebanon, Moreira da Silva said.
OL,16,FHe warned that the number of hungry
OL,17,Fpeople is likely to increase by tens
OL,18,Fof millions over the course of the
OL,19,Fyear, as the impact of the war widens.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30618
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1774293066
OL,3,CPM and Trump have 'constructive' call
OL,4,Cas US deadline to Iran looms
OL,6,FAsia has been the hardest hit by
OL,7,Fenergy shortages as a result of the
OL,8,Fwar, with the majority of oil and
OL,9,Fliquefied natural gas passing through
OL,10,Fthe Strait of Hormuz destined for the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FIn Manila, the Philippines, a group of
OL,14,Fprotesters condemned the war outside
OL,15,Fthe US embassy on Monday.
OL,17,F"No country will be immune to the
OL,18,Feffects of this crisis if it continues
OL,19,Fto go in this direction," said Fatih
OL,20,FBirol, the head of the Paris-based
OL,21,FInternational Energy Agency, on Monday.
OL,26,@{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
